    <li>E-mail</li>
    <li>Instant Messaging</li>
    <li>Blogging</li>
    <li>Social Media</li>
    <li>Marketing</li>
    <li>Networking</li>
    <li>Resource Sharing</li>
    <li>Audio and Video Streaming</li>
    </ul>


 
